Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user

Class Faculty

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.User
      • edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.Faculty
  • public class Faculty
extends User
    Class defining Faculty subclass of User superclass, modeled after the Student class, with the key difference being that Faculty has a maxCourses field rather than a maxCredits field.
    Author:
    Hunter Pruitt
